            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Pro salute <expan><abbr>Imp</abbr><ex>eratorum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Caesari</abbr><ex>s</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>uci</ex></expan> Septimi Severi et <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arci</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Aur</abbr><ex>eli</ex></expan> Antonini <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>Aug<am>g</am></abbr><ex>ustorum</ex></expan> et <expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>ubli</ex></expan> Septimi Gaetae <note>sic</note> <expan><abbr>Caesari</abbr><ex>s</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arcus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Aur</abbr><ex>elius</ex></expan> Rufinus evocatus <expan><abbr>Aug<am>g</am></abbr><ex>ustorum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>ostrorum</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/>Sancto Deo Invicto speleum constituit cum <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>mil</abbr><ex>itibus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pr</abbr><ex>aetorianis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Fl</abbr><ex>avio</ex></expan> Clarino <expan><abbr>Ael</abbr><ex>io</ex></expan> Messio <expan><abbr>Aur</abbr><ex>elio</ex></expan> Iuliano
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Auf dem Foto sind die Buchstaben oft kaum erkannbar. (B): Abweichende Textgestaltung der Ergänzungen in Z. 1.</p>
            </div>
